M hnh tng dn s theo cp s nhn

Gi nh quan st mt dn s gi nh trong 2 nm. Gi s c 100 ngi trong nm u v 150 ngi trong nm th 2. Khi , tc tng dn s (population growth rate) trong 2 nm bng \(\frac{N2}{N1}=1.5\).

Tng qut, tc tng trng hng nm, \(\lambda\) bng s lng ngi trong 1 nm so vi nm trc :

\[ \lambda = \frac{N_{t+1}}{N_t} \]

Nu tc tng trng ny khng i trong \(t\) nm v quy m dn s ban u l \(N_{0}\), th quy m dn s ti nm \(t\) bng:

\[ N_{t}=N_{0}\lambda^t \]

y l m hnh geometric population growth, tc l dn s tng hnh hc theo cc bc thi gian ri rc v tc tng trng khng i.

Exponential population growth (tng trng dn s theo cp s nhn) xy ra khi dn s gia tng trong thi gian lin tc vi tc tng trng khng i, \(r\):

\[ N_{t} = N_{0}e^{rt} \]

y, \(r\) l tc tng trng tc thi (instantaneous rate of growth) bng t l sinh (s sinh trn mi c nhn) tr i t l cht (s cht trn mi c nhn) ti bt k khong thi gian no.

M hnh tng trng theo cp s nhn v hnh hc rt ging nhau, tr mt s tnh cht ton hc. Vi 1 n v thi gian nht nh, chng ta c th chuyn i qua 2 m hnh d dng. Lu \(\lambda = e^r\) v \(\ln\lambda = r\)

By gi, lp m hnh tng trng dn s (h Khc) trong 1120 nm vi dn s ban u l 100 (nm 900) v dn s thi im cui l 22000 (nm 2020, theo thng k tnh c), t tnh c \(\lambda = 1.0052\). Gn hng s (\(N_{0}\) v \(\lambda\)) v lp m hnh tng trng dn s ti thi im \(N_{t}\) vi \(t\) nm trong khong t 0 (nm 900) n 1120 (nm 2020).

N0 = 100
lambda = 1.0048
t = 0:1120

Thay i tc tng trng dn s

By gi, lp m hnh dn s vi cc t l tng trng khc nhau, \(\lambda\). Vi 2 tham s thay i (\(t\) v \(\lambda\)). iu ngha l chng ta cn u ra l mt ma trn, vi 1 tham s (\(t\)) theo hng v mt tham s khc (\(\lambda\)) theo ct.

Sau , chng ta cn xc nh mt s \(\lambda\) ( y, l 1.0044, 1.0046, 1.0048, 1.0050 v 1.052) sau chy tt c cc kh nng theo cng thc t l tng trng dn s. Hm ny s tr v mt vector hoc mt ma trn, ty thuc vo dng n gin nht.

N0 = 100
lambda = seq(1.0044, 1.0052, by=0.0002)
t = 0:1120
N = sapply(lambda, function(lambda) N0 * lambda^t)

Kt qu thu c l 1 ma trn vi 1121 hng tng ng vi \(t\) = 0 n 1120 v 5 ct tng ng vi 5 gi tr ca \(\lambda\) (1.0044, 1.0046, 1.0048, 1.0050, 1.052). Biu phn b dn s c biu din nh sau:

matplot(t, N, las = 1, xaxt='n', type = "l", pch = 19, xaxt='n', xlab="Nm", ylab="", main="Phn b dn s h Khc t nm 900 n 2020")
#plot(t, N, type = "l", pch = 19, las = 1, xaxt='n')

Dn s tng khi \(\lambda\) > 1 v ngc li.

Vi tc tng trng tc thi (instantaneous rate of growth), \(r = \ln\lambda\):

  • Dn s khng thay i khi \(\lambda\) = 1 hoc \(r\) = 0
  • Dn s tng khi \(\lambda\) > 1 hoc \(r\) > 0
  • Dn s gim khi \(\lambda\) < 1 hoc \(r\) < 0

M hnh ngu nhin

Chng ta ang gi nh rng tc gia tng dn s l khng i theo thi gian. iu ny r rng khng phi l ng trong hu ht cc qun th t nhin. Ngay c khi b qua cc c ch ph thuc vo mt , t l tng trng ph bin cng dao ng do cc ngun ngu nhin khc nhau (tc l ngu nhin). Mt ngun chnh ca tnh ngu nhin trong t l gia tng dn s l mi trng ngu nhin: tc l s bin ng ngu nhin ca t l gia tng dn s do cc nm tt v xu.

Gi s mt qun th c t l tng dn s n nh tc l t l tng trng tc thi trung bnh, \(\bar{r}\) = 0. Nhng t l tng trng thc t dao ng xung quanh mc trung bnh ny vi mt s phng sai, \(\sigma_{r}^2\) = 0.01. Do , i vi mi bc thi gian (gi s, 1120), ta c th ly ngu nhin mt s t phn phi chun vi gi tr trung bnh l 0 v phng sai l 0,01 (hoc lch chun \(sd = \sqrt{var} = 0.1\)), nh sau:

set.seed(2)
rs = rnorm(1120, mean = 0, sd = 0.1)
hist(rs, xlab = "r")

c tnh nht qun trong mc ch lp m hnh, ta chuyn i phn phi t l tng trng ny thnh t l tng trng dn s ri rc \(\lambda\), c biu th bng \(e^r\). Theo , phn phi \(\lambda\) trong trng hp ny l:

hist(exp(rs), xlab = "lambda", main = "Histogram of lambdas")

2 phn phi nhn kh ging nhau, nhng phn phi trn (phn phi ca \(r\)) l 1 phn phi chun tp trung quanh 0, v phn phi di (phn phi ca \(\lambda\)) l phn phi log-normal ngha l, log ca gi tr l 1 phn phi chun tp trung quanh 1.

Chng ta c th ly trc tip phn phi ca \(\lambda\) t phn phi log-normal:

set.seed(2)
lambdas = rlnorm(1120, meanlog = 0, sdlog = 0.1)
round(lambdas, 2)

Chng ta s dng phng php ngu nhin v t l gia tng dn s ny m hnh s gia tng dn s. D bo dn s trong 1120 nm di s gia tng dn s hnh hc vi \(\lambda\) = 1.0046 v \(N_{0}\)=100.

S dng vng lp tnh \(N_{t}\) cho mi bc thi gian \(t\) v lu tr n di dng vector.

N0 = 100  #initial population size
times = 1120  #number of years into the future
N = vector(length = times)  #empty vector to store pop. sizes
N[1] = N0  #initial population size should be the first N
lambda = 1.0048  #growth rate
# start loop: Take previous year's N and multiply by lambda
for (t in 2:times) {
    N[t] = N[t - 1] * lambda
}

plot(1:times, N, type = "l", pch = 19, las = 1, xaxt='n', xlab="Nm", ylab="")
axis(side=1, at=c(0, 200, 400, 600, 800, 1000, 1120), labels=c("900", "1100", "1300", "1500", "1700", "1900", "2020"))
abline(v=1120, col="red", lty=2, lwd=2)

set.seed(2)
N0 = 100  #initial population size
times = 1120  #number of years into the future
N = vector(length = times)  #empty vector to store pop. sizes
N[1] = N0  #initial population size should be the first N

# lambdas--we only need 19 numbers because growth only
# happens between 2 years.
lambda = rlnorm(times - 1, meanlog = 0, sdlog = 0.1)

# start loop: Take previous year's N and multiply by lambda
for (t in 2:times) {
    N[t] = N[t - 1] * lambda[t - 1]
}

plot(1:times, N, type = "l", pch = 19, las = 1, xaxt='n', xlab="Nm", ylab="")
axis(side=1, at=c(0, 200, 400, 600, 800, 1000, 1120), labels=c("900", "1100", "1300", "1500", "1700", "1900", "2020"))

# multiple simulations

    times = 1120
    N0 = 100

        N[t] = N[t - 1] * lambda[t - 1]
    }
    N
})
